<p>On 03/13/2004 at 1100 hours the SCP-682 observation booth was cleared of all personnel without BASILISK certification, under the authority of Senior Agent Vanessa Rider. At 1115 an image of the <a href="/scp-2140">SCP-2140</a> glyph was projected onto the wall of the SCP-682 containment enclosure.</p>
